{
  "texts": [
    "For each query, the \"New Chat\" option was selected to avoid any influence from previous interactions.",
    "The \"Regenerate Response\" feature was not utilized to rely on the first response generated.",
    "Evaluation of the ChatGPT Generated ContentThe evaluation of the AI-generated content was conducted by the first author, who holds an MD degree since 2007 with a specialty degree in laboratory medicine.",
    "This assessment employed the CLEAR (focusing on three components: Completeness, Accuracy (Lack of false information and Evidence-based content), and Appropriateness and Relevance [27].",
    "Each component was assessed using a 5-point Likert scale, ranging from 5 (excellent) to 1 (poor), to quantify the quality of responses."
  ]
}